# Matthew Parlee | Instructional Design & Learning Experience Portfolio

This repository hosts the code for my professional portfolio, developed using a 
collaborative AI-workflow (Lovable + Gemini) to showcase high-impact learning 
solutions and performance enablement strategies.

## 🔗 [View Live Portfolio Here](https://matthewparlee.github.io)

## Featured Case Studies
* **Digital Transformation:** Advisor enablement simulations for financial services.
* **Health & Safety:** Experiential learning programs for legislative evaluation.
* **Accredited Training:** Standardized disinfection certification frameworks.

## Technical Approach
* **Hosting:** Optimized for performance and deployed via GitHub Pages.
* **Strategy:** Focused on evidence-based learning science and cognitive load reduction.
